snippet.title: Doctor Who: Battle of Time Android Gameplay [1080p/60fps]
snippet.description:
Doctor Who: Battle of Time by BANDAI NAMCO (Card Game)
Download | https://doctor-who-battle-of-time.en.uptodown.com/android?utm_source=youtube.com&utm_medium=description&utm_campaign=traffic_ac
SUBSCRIBE FOR MORE HD VIDEOS → https://goo.gl/Pz1CBK
Google play | https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.bandainamcoent.google.doctorwho

Description | Doctor Who: Battle of Time is a card game in the purest Hearthstone style, in which players will have to help the Doctor save the universe. Again. For this it will be necessary to fight El Silencio or the Daleks, among many other enemies. Doctor Who: Battle of Time is a very entertaining game of card duels, which has a great atmosphere and a very extensive 'story mode'. The game also has more than two hundred different cards, almost all characters and aliens that have appeared in the series.
